OL,3,CPassengers travelling to London from
OL,4,CEast Midlands warned of delays
OL,6,FMajor engineering work is going to
OL,7,Faffect passengers travelling to London
OL,8,Fthrough the East Midlands over the
OL,9,Ffestive period.
OL,11,FTrain operator East Midlands Railway
OL,12,F(EMR) said the work would start today
OL,13,Fand continue to Sunday 29 December.
OL,15,FPassengers are being advised to plan
OL,16,Fahead as parts of the Midland Mainline
OL,17,Fbetween London St Pancras and Bedford
OL,18,Fwill be closed.
