OL,3,CPassengers travelling to London from
OL,4,CEast Midlands warned of delays
OL,6,FEMR say that services will be
OL,7,F"severely disrupted", with journeys in
OL,8,FNottingham and Derby even involving
OL,9,Frail replacement buses.
OL,11,FBut the operator promises that the
OL,12,Fengineering work will be necessary to
OL,13,Fimprove services in the long run.
