OL,3,CPassengers travelling to London from
OL,4,CEast Midlands warned of delays
OL,6,FMark Budden, route director for
OL,7,FNetwork Rail's East Midlands route
OL,8,Fsaid: "We're sorry that this essential
OL,9,Fwork will cause significant disruption
OL,10,Fto journeys for many people over the
OL,11,Ffestive period. We've worked hard to
OL,12,Fmake sure the work will be completed
OL,13,Fas quickly and safely as possible.
OL,15,F"We're deploying hundreds of people to
OL,16,Fcarry out dozens of jobs to prevent
OL,17,Ffurther disruption at another time.
OL,18,FOnce complete this essential work will
OL,19,Fmean passengers will have smoother,
OL,20,Ffaster and more reliable journeys.
