OL,3,CPassengers travelling to London from
OL,4,CEast Midlands warned of delays
OL,6,F"Timetables will start to be published
OL,7,Fthis weekend so we're advising anyone
OL,8,Fplanning to travel between Saturday 21
OL,9,Fand Sunday 29 December to check your
OL,10,Fwhole journey, including connections
OL,11,Fas soon as you can.
OL,13,F"Though most of the network will be
OL,14,Fopen as normal, there is engineering
OL,15,Fwork on several parts of the network
OL,16,Fon different dates over the festive
OL,17,Fperiod."
